channel.title: I want to work with you
channel.description:
Hi!
I love the 3d modeling and I want to contribute to the project blackmesa.
I studied game design and development engineering, my passion is computer generated graphics and I want and need to work with people I keep learning.
Please contact me for work!
Thanks

item.description:
Crypt19 is right. You might try to send a email but if you haven’t done anything before, it’s not likely you’ll be picked.

item.title: I want to work with you
item.dc:creator: Crypt
item.description:
Think you got the wrong section. Test Chamber is for contributions to the mod you’ve already made and would like to submit. There’s also a wiki page for this topic, but considering the game is out I wouldn’t imagine they need new team members, but who knows.
